## D18 SSE Frontend Event Router
**Status:** implemented
**Module:** `packages/auto-forge-ui/src/composables/useEventRouter.ts`
**Depends on:** A5, D9

```typescript
interface SSEEvent {
  type: 'run_started' | 'step_advanced' | 'spec_written'
       | 'gate_reached' | 'gate_resolved'
       | 'handoff_submitted' | 'run_completed'
  runId: string
  payload: Record<string, unknown>
}

function useEventRouter() {
  function handleEvent(event: SSEEvent, currentView: 'chat' | 'specs' | 'relay')
}
```

| Event | Chat View | Specs View | Relay View |
|---|---|---|---|
| `run_started` | System message | — | Highlight run |
| `step_advanced` | **NO action** (ambient only) | — | Animate node |
| `spec_written` | — | Flash changed section | — |
| `gate_reached` | SecretaryMessage | GateBanner | GatePanel |
| `gate_resolved` | Collapse message | Hide banner | Hide panel |
| `handoff_submitted` | — | — | Append to Live Log |
| `run_completed` | ReportCard | Update Reports | Mark run done |


